Upgrades the connection to a WebSocket for real-time admin support chat. Accessible by super_admin, admin, and support roles.

**Inbound frame shape:**
```json
{ "type": "message", "ticket_id": "<uuid>", "content": "hello" }
{ "type": "read",    "ticket_id": "<uuid>" }
{ "type": "typing",  "ticket_id": "<uuid>" }
```

**Outbound frame types:** `message`, `read`, `typing`, `error`

